<h2 class="w3-center w3-content">Fortnite Battle Royale, developed by Epic Games, is a Battle Royale video game launched in 2017. It takes place on an island where 100 players battle it out until only one survives. Players land with no equipment, must find weapons and resources, and build structures to protect themselves. The island undergoes regular changes, introducing new challenges and places of interest.</h2>
</br>
