<h2 class="w3-center w3-content">The game is distinguished by its construction aspect, allowing players to create structures in real time. Seasons, each lasting around ten weeks, bring changes to the map, cosmetics and challenges. The Battle Pass, available for purchase, offers exclusive rewards for completing objectives.</h2>
